@startuml
title Viaverse Dispute / Refund / Payout — State Diagram

[*] --> OPENED
OPENED --> VALIDATING : validate
VALIDATING --> EVIDENCE_COLLECTION : valid
VALIDATING --> REJECTED_INVALID : invalid
EVIDENCE_COLLECTION --> ADMIN_REVIEW : submitted / timeout
ADMIN_REVIEW --> RESOLVED_REFUND : refund
ADMIN_REVIEW --> RESOLVED_PAYOUT : payout
ADMIN_REVIEW --> RESOLVED_SPLIT : split
ADMIN_REVIEW --> ESCALATED : legal/complex
ESCALATED --> ADMIN_REVIEW : return
RESOLVED_REFUND --> CLOSED : audit + events
RESOLVED_PAYOUT --> CLOSED : audit + events
RESOLVED_SPLIT --> CLOSED : audit + events
REJECTED_INVALID --> [*]
CLOSED --> [*]

note bottom
When dispute is not closed, payout must remain blocked.
Refund/release/split are terminal resolution actions with idempotency keys.
end note
@enduml
